sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant W as Browser<br/>(verify.fivucsas.com)
    participant API as Identity Core API
    participant BIO as Biometric Service<br/>(internal-only)
    participant PGB as PostgreSQL<br/>biometric_db (pgvector)

    note over BIO: continued from part (a):<br/>frame passed the passive-liveness floor

    BIO->>BIO: face detection -- MTCNN<br/>(400 if none or multiple)
    BIO->>BIO: quality gate, verify floor 50<br/>(stricter than enrollment's 40)

    alt quality below 50
        BIO-->>API: 200 verified=false<br/>"image quality too low"
        API-->>W: step failed -- retry capture
    else quality passed
        BIO->>BIO: Facenet512 embedding<br/>(DeepFace, 512-dim)
        BIO->>PGB: fetch enrolled embedding<br/>(Fernet-decrypt ciphertext,<br/>404 if user not enrolled)
        BIO->>BIO: cosine distance vs threshold:<br/>verified = distance below 0.4 (prod) --<br/>0.55 when enrollment older than 2 years
        BIO->>BIO: anti-spoof assembler (13 analyzers)<br/>+ EAR veto (avg EAR below 0.18)

        alt spoof veto fires (even on a matching face)
            BIO-->>API: 403 ANTISPOOF_BLOCKED {reason}
            API->>API: MFA step FAILED + audit
            API-->>W: blocked: spoof suspected
        else clean
            BIO-->>API: 200 {verified, distance,<br/>threshold, confidence}
            note right of API: handler trusts ONLY the<br/>server "verified" flag --<br/>no client-side fallback
            alt verified = true
                API->>API: MFA step COMPLETED + audit --<br/>amr += "face"
                API-->>W: next step -- or, after the last step,<br/>JWT access (RS256) + rotating refresh token
            else verified = false
                API->>API: MFA step FAILED + audit<br/>(counts toward 5-strike lockout)
                API-->>W: face does not match
            end
        end
    end
